---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About HLK Nasal Strips — 20+ Years Manufacturing Excellence | Factory & OEM"
  description="Quanzhou Honglinkai New Material Co., Ltd. — a leading nasal strip manufacturer in China with 5,000m² facility, FDA/CE/ISO 13485 certified. 20+ years of adhesive technology expertise."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About HLK</h1>
      <p>The manufacturing partner behind successful nasal strip brands worldwide.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Company Story ===== -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="product-grid">
        <img src="/images/HLK_Lifestyle_Female_Model.jpg" alt="HLK Factory & Product" loading="lazy" style="width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: var(--radius-xl); min-height: 350px; object-fit: cover;" />
        <div>
          <h2>20+ Years of Adhesive Technology</h2>
          <p>Quanzhou Honglinkai New Material Co., Ltd. (HLK) was founded in 2005 with a single mission: to produce the world's most reliable adhesive products for health and wellness applications.</p>
          <p>What started as a small tape manufacturing workshop has grown into a 5,000m&sup2; modern production facility equipped with automated production lines, in-house R&amp;D laboratory, and a dedicated quality control team.</p>
          <p>Today, HLK ships to 30+ countries across the US, EU, South America, Middle East, and Asia-Pacific. We are the trusted OEM partner for brands sold in Walmart, CVS, Amazon, and pharmacy chains worldwide.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Facility ===== -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--gray-50);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Manufacturing Facility</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">State-of-the-art production lines with strict quality management.</p>

      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">🏗️</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">5,000m&sup2; Workshop</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Climate-controlled production environment. Separate zones for raw material storage, production, packaging, and finished goods warehouse.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">🤖</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">Automated Lines</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">5 fully automated production lines with precision cutting, adhesive application, and packaging. Capacity: 2M+ units per month.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">🔬</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">In-House R&amp;D Lab</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Adhesion testing, skin irritation testing, accelerated aging tests, packaging integrity verification — all performed on-site.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Certifications ===== -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Certifications</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Quality, safety, and compliance — verified by international authorities.</p>

      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--blue-600); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">FDA</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">FDA Registered</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Our facility and products are registered with the U.S. Food and Drug Administration, meeting all requirements for medical devices sold in the United States.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--blue-600); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">CE</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">CE Marked</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Our nasal strips comply with EU Medical Device Regulation (MDR) 2017/745, enabling free sale across the European Union.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--blue-600); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">ISO</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">ISO 13485</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Medical device quality management system certified. Every batch is produced and tested under strict quality standards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--blue-600); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">SGS</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">SGS Tested</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Third-party testing for material safety, biocompatibility, and performance by SGS — the world's leading testing laboratory.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--blue-600); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">RoHS</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">RoHS Compliant</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">All raw materials are RoHS-compliant, ensuring no hazardous substances are present in our products.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🤝</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">Audited Factory</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">We welcome factory audits from clients and third-party inspection agencies. Transparency builds trust.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Visit Our Factory or Request Samples</h2>
    <p>We welcome factory visits and third-party audits. Let's discuss how we can support your business.</p>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">Contact Our Team</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/8619559068109" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg" style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); color: white;">WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
